The optimization of the precoding scheme is aimed at improving the performance of the network, which falls under the purview of social and information networks. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper deals with designing a precoding scheme for MU-MIMO OFDM systems, which are commonly used for multimedia applications such as video streaming.
